task.summary: Added stubbers and finders. Now the injection of a code to the beginning of the loop is done.
Added a MethodStubber and refactored the whole hierarchy of the stubbers.
Fixed assignment stubbing and a bug causing the copying of the rest of the loop's body when stubbing it.
Fully implemented the first version of the Archive.
Changed the __AS__ stub tto recieve pairs of "lhs" and rhs (values).
- Fixed the exec to include globals(). - Compiled the code before executing it. - Converted graphics to python3 (with 2to3) - Added __str__ to the Tetris classes. - Added a __str__ to Archive class.
Changed to name of the example fie to a relative path.
Changed the __FLI__ to check |n| instead on n

- Changed the engine to print the stacktrace in case of an exception in the execution of the PaLaDiNized code. - Changed the __str__ of Archive to print lists as they are (with the []). - Changed the archive to use deep-copy of values instead of shallow-copy.
